Name: Azurill
Description: A Pokemon that lives by water. It moves quickly on land by bouncing on its big tail.

Name: Charizard
Description: Spits fire that is hot enough to melt boulders. Known to unintentionally cause forest fires

Name: Eevee
Description: Because its genetic makeup is irregular. it quickly changes its form due to a variety of causes.

Name: Zoroark
Description: This extremely rare Pokemon is a different color than usual. It is very hard to find.

Name: Mewtwo
Description: A scientist created this Pokemon after years of horrific gene-splicing and DNA engineering experiments.

Name: Mudkip
Description: To alert it. the fin on its head senses the flow of water. It has the strength to lift boulders.

Name: Bayleef
Description: The buds that ring its neck give off a spicy aroma that perks people up.

Name: Magikarp
Description: In the distant past. it was stronger than its horribly weak descendants that exist today.

Name: Abra
Description: Using its ability to read minds. it will identify impending danger and teleport to safety.

Name: Luxray
Description: It can see clearly through walls to track down its prey and seek its lost young.
